{"tid":790733,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大力沽萬洲國際!為被活埋的豬隻報仇!","createTime":"2018-08-23T09:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T16:41:18.000Z","uid":116471,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c391b1cc6c971da920d425a137942360ed68b858","tid":790733,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:02:44.000Z","msg":"《新京報》報道，周三遼寧省瀋陽市瀋北新區一處養有383頭豬的養豬場通報有47頭病豬死亡。農業農村部抽取樣本測試，昨日上午11時經中國動物衛生與流行病學中心證實為非洲豬瘟。農業農村部、遼寧省委按去年制定的《非洲豬瘟疫情應急預案》啟動二級應急響應，活埋疫區內913頭活豬，對病死豬及相關飼料、墊料等可能被污染物品作火燒等無害化處理，同時禁止所有生豬及易受感染的動物及產品運入或流出封鎖區，全市範圍的活豬運輸暫停。"},{"pid":"05dc0a8d0c5f3de4d479ad56dce1df44b8d13c57","tid":790733,"uid":79484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:04:21.000Z","msg":"你有貨咩"},{"pid":"c1bc63184bba4eb77228793bdc91182640c43240","tid":790733,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"05dc0a8d0c5f3de4d479ad56dce1df44b8d13c57","tid":790733,"uid":79484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:04:21.000Z","msg":"你有貨咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"已由9蚊開始沽空!"},{"pid":"35feee0a5c9c868cd36d3aefc04964a830b64122","tid":790733,"uid":44980,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:08:25.000Z","msg":"放心豬沒有真正被活埋～好似係<br />\n申利：唔食午餐肉"},{"pid":"0a2bb280b60b74f4cf6603d5dda2be3224363711","tid":790733,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35feee0a5c9c868cd36d3aefc04964a830b64122","tid":790733,"uid":44980,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:08:25.000Z","msg":"放心豬沒有真正被活埋～好似係<br />\n申利：唔食午餐肉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:10:17.000Z","msg":"咁無陰功活埋豬，唔沽到4蚊都唔會停手。"},{"pid":"9f116eb1978418e0229c1db4bdb03081a6c86df9","tid":790733,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:30:35.000Z","msg":"支持樓豬"},{"pid":"ae2d96d8f03ae6b0f224501f1a4f21f847b9fd1d","tid":790733,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20